thread.title: BRIEF-Emperia Holding Q4 Net Profit Down At 10.1 Million Zlotys

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Emperia Holding Q4 Net Profit Down At 10.1 Million Zlotys
text:
Feb 27 (Reuters) - EMPERIA HOLDING SA
* REPORTED ON MONDAY Q4 NET PROFIT AT 10.1 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 15.8 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* Q4 REVENUE AT 699.3 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 627.0 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* Q4 OPERATING PROFIT AT 10.7 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 19.6 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
Source text: bit.ly/2CMnC2n
